WEBVTT

00:08:27.958 --> 00:08:30.208
and targeted for generations.

00:08:30.917 --> 00:08:32.726
These are the frontlines.

00:08:32.750 --> 00:08:34.792
This is where we start.

00:08:35.500 --> 00:08:40.351
We must establish a new social attitude
to see migration as a benefit,

00:08:40.375 --> 00:08:43.226
a necessity for our global survival,

00:08:43.250 --> 00:08:46.167
not as a threat
to our individual privilege.

00:08:46.958 --> 00:08:51.184
Collective resilience means developing
cities that can receive people

00:08:51.208 --> 00:08:52.893
and provide housing,

00:08:52.917 --> 00:08:55.809
food, water, health care

00:08:55.833 --> 00:08:57.851
and the freedom from overpolicing

00:08:57.875 --> 00:08:59.143
for everyone,

00:08:59.167 --> 00:09:00.518
no matter who they are,